posting_body: ['We are happy to provide IN PERSON TOURS with your confirmed tour appointment for anyone looking to call Courtland Place and Rainier Valley home.', 'Call or message us to schedule a viewing TODAY !!', 'See, Sign and $ave...$45.00 application fee, a $500.00 security deposit and 1st months rent move you in.', '***ONE MONTH FREE WITH A 12 MONTH LEASE***', 'Important Deets:', '**', 'Availability - Now (Sign for immediate Move-in or for as late as 8/15/2022)', '**', 'Pets: Kitties and Small Dogs (Max - 40 #)', '** Leasing options: 12 month Leases currently offered', '** Apply for $45 per prospective resident', '**', 'Holding Deposit: $400.00 (One bedroom) $500.00 (Two Bedroom)', 'Appliances: W/ D outlets in select apartments, all new refrigerators and stoves', 'Utilities Cost: Independently billed - Electric | WSG included', 'Parking type: Outdoor Parking Street Parking (Free)', 'Parking type: Garage - (Free) Waitlist only', 'Exterior: Balcony/patio select apartments', 'Wired for: Cable-ready, High-speed internet', 'Limited Entry Access: Elevator, Controlled access, Disability access', 'Our Flat features a Galley Style Kitchen, all new Floors, Appliances and Abundant Natural Light.', 'This is a Rainier Valley Gem.', 'Our Amazing TWO BEDROOM APARTMENT is OUT THE DOOR AT ONLY $1152.00.', 'Pick-up the phone and confirm a showing that best meets your busy on the go schedule.', 'Have further questions ??', 'Please inquire with our friendly team before joining us for an on-site walk-about.', 'Courtland Place at Rainier Court', '3621 33 Ave S', 'Seattle, Washington 98144', '** Pictures representative of actual apartment offer for lease']
